Story: An existing user wants to log into FreeWater
  1. Start with login screen
    - Button to link create account user story
    - Button to link forgot password user story
  2. User will input the email and password associated with their account
  3. We will then Authenticate User Account
    - Good Path: user account exists and password matches   
        Direct User to home screen, button to user story 3,4,5
    - Bad Path: user account cannot be found or password does not match 
        Throw error message requesting user to check inputted info and allow them to try again
